title: Surreal Convergence
description:
In surreal convergence, dreams align,
Echoed silhouettes in twilight's design.

title: Ascendancy of the Ancients
description:
The mighty ancients shed their chains, to the sky, they claim their part,
In the heavens' endless canvas, they paint their immortal art.

title: Shadow Griffith
description:
In shadows deep, she hides her might,
Her eyes, a void, bereft of light.
